  "id": "RAW_6a3d430b",
  "title": "津渡生科邓司伟：「AI+生物制造」到底是什么？全链智能已经实现",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODEzMjIyMA==&mid=2247730805&idx=2&sn=855eb011c63586e9e9c45ee03e3802ae",
  "date": "2026-01-21 12:26:00",
